# Copy to ".env.local" in the project root (see also fcm-server/DEPLOY.md).
# Vite loads .env.local for dev, build, and desktop:build.
#
# Development: keep http://localhost:3002 (npm run dev starts the ZATCA process).
# Production build: set your public HTTPS API (no trailing slash).
# VITE_ZATCA_SERVICE_URL=https://zatca-api.yourdomain.com
